name: Dub Caesar x Phood Court Studios Presents "Studio Sessions With"
description:
THIS IS NOT FOR SALE!!!  IT'S A FREE DOWNLOAD AT DUBCAESAR.COM!!!

STUDIO SESSIONS WITH ...
Hosted by DJ NoPhrillz and DJ Benja Styles

This is DCA's first mixtape project that wanted to showcase some of the up and coming talent in the Philly area as well as to feature a few already established emcee's such as FREEWAY, REEF THE LOST CAUZE, AND TEK from Smif n Wessun.

name: Dub Caesar Apparel Presents MAZON'S "Maintaining"
description:
THIS IS NOT FOR SALE.  It is a FREE DOWNLOAD at www.DUBCAESAR.com

This is a project featuring promising Harrisburg artist MAZON.  Mazon is a talented emcee who's stays true to hip hop and emceeing which he clearly displays throughout this project.  Take a minute to download this mixtape and to get a little more familiar with him.
